The '''[[natural science]]s''' are those [[Branches of science|branches of]] [[Empirical evidence|empirical]] [[science]] that produce a comprehension of the [[Natural environment|natural world]] through the use of [[data]] [[Data collection|collected]] from it by [[observation]] and [[measurement]] to construct [[Deterministic system|deterministic]] and/or [[stochastic]] [[quantitative]] [[Scientific modelling|models]] of its phenomena.

